data.description: Welcome to 501 Walnut Street, Sunbury!   In the heart of Sunbury, this charming 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom single-family home at 501 Walnut Street has both comfort and convenience.  With 702 square feet of living space, this home is on a spacious corner lot with a fenced-in yard and lots of opportunity. The living area features modern ceiling fans and the layout is well designed to maximize every square foot. The built-in 1-car garage ensures your vehicle stays protected from the elements and the front porch offers views of the neighborhood.  There is also tons of potential space in the lower level to add another bedroom or office area. Don't miss this opportunity in Sunbury! Schedule a viewing today.
